  "texts": [
    "We gathered information of 83 tourist attractions across 15 cities, 846 intra-city and 3903 inter-city transportation routes.",
    "Based on this foundation, we employed a combination of manual curation and code-assisted method to construct 364 distinct samples, exclusively reserved as the test set.",
    "Each sample represents a unique travel planning scenario, encompassing various combinations of cities, attractions, transportation modes, and scheduling constraints.",
    "Detailed statistics can be found in Appendix A.",
    "Our benchmark encompasses three distinct task types, each anchored by a central storyline from which numerous data samples emerge."
